title: SX-Level错误
author: nai_niu
txt_content:
SX-Level错误 在处理经验的时候没有增加 
13:23:19] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum] [Yum 事件监控] 插件 SX-Level 处理 PlayerExpChangeEvent 事件时发生异常!
[13:23:19] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum] 异常名称: java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
[13:23:19] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum] 异常说明: Experience progress must be between 0.0 and 1.0 (1.93)
